IWithSecondaryNetworkInterface.WithExistingSecondaryNetworkInterface Method

Definition

Namespace:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent.VirtualMachine.Update
Assembly:
Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent.dll

In this Article

Associate an existing network interface with the virtual machine. Note this method's effect is additive, i.e. each time it is used, the new secondary network interface added to the virtual machine.

public Microsoft.Azure.Management.Compute.Fluent.VirtualMachine.Update.IUpdate WithExistingSecondaryNetworkInterface (Microsoft.Azure.Management.Network.Fluent.INetworkInterface networkInterface);
Parameters
networkInterface
INetworkInterface

An existing network interface.

Returns
IUpdate

To be added.
